create a bluemix account:
https://console.ng.bluemix.net/registration/?Target=https%3A%2F%2Fconsole.ng.bluemix.net%2Flogin

install the command line interfaces from :
https://console.ng.bluemix.net/docs/cli/index.html#cli

go through this simpe tutorial
https://console.ng.bluemix.net/docs/containers/container_gettingstarted.html#container_gettingstarted_tutorial

note that you have to install the container plugins:
from https://console.ng.bluemix.net/docs/containers/container_gettingstarted_tutorial_lesson1.html#container_gettingstarted_tutorial_lesson_1
..install the cli pugin for bluemix containers
cf install-plugin https://static-ice.ng.bluemix.net/ibm-containers-linux_x64
cf install-plugin https://static-ice.ng.bluemix.net/ibm-containers-windows_x64.exe
